title: Aces Wild: Maniac Brawling Action!
notes:
First time setup took abnormally long, and then it paused indefinitely on "Preparing to launch." Terminal is spamming "eventfd: Too many open files."

Running steam with ulimit -n 4096 fixed that problem, but then it gets past that part and just hangs again before the window is created. No abnormal error messages in the Terminal.

After that, I killed all wine/proton-related processes and tried launching again. It goes through the first time setup again, and then promptly crashes. Steam terminal output of crash here: https://pastebin.com/eX4rjaQ8
